description: Redevelopment of the site in the following manner: Refurbishment and conversion of existing building and caretaker's house on the Townmead Road frontage; the erection of a 2-storey building (with additional accommodation at roof level) on the Elbe Street frontage, a part 3-storey, part 4-storey building on the Elswick Street frontage, and a part 4-storey, part 5-storey building on the Bagley's Lane frontage, providing a total of 109 residential units; provision of 87 on-site car parking spaces (49 in a basement car park accessed from Bagley's Lane).
